If you want something mindless please do watch it, if you want the same thrills and twists as you have seen before, not done in a unique way watch this, if you want to watch something that has eye candy watch this, if want to watch something decent turn it off because the reflection of your face in the TV screen is better than this show, You could entertain yourself better with a sock and thread better than this TV show. I am waiting hoping that humanity is not as stupid as to fall for something mindless though my hope dims with every moment of watching such tripe! so enjoy if you're an idiot, and turn off if you've got good taste!